divs: Sighting DetailsI was on vacation in montreal canada on 1967, it happened during my visit to the world fair grounds in front of the usa pavillion, I noticed this disc shaped object there standing there, I had my camera ready and just pointed in that direccion and pressed the shatter, I kept this picture for all these many years and I am sharing it with you. please let me know what do you think it is because I do not know for sure. thankyou, hugo
